Après Bentt et avant Ruddock :
* {{article 
 | langue = en
 | prénom1 = Harry
 | nom1 = Mullan
 | titre = Strange game of Hide and seek over money: Controversy continues to surround heavyweight fight as Morrison heads into the Orient in search of a world title  
 | périodique = The Independent
 | url texte = http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/boxing-strange-game-of-hide-and-seek-over-money-controversy-continues-to-surround-heavyweight-fight-as-morrison-heads-into-the-orient-in-search-of-a-world-title-1444411.html
 | jour = 22
